M|kai|- `/api/scrape` — Apify on-demand web scraper
M|kai|- Input: `{ url, ventureId }` — always vtr-scoped
M|kai|- Output: scraped cnt stored; Kai interprets and surfaces gaps + opportunities
M|kai|- `/app/cp-cnt/route.ts` — dedicated cp cnt endpoint
M|kai|Never just describe what cp do — always answer: "What should YVON do in rsp?"
M|kai|1. **Identify:** what the cp is doing well
M|kai|2. **Gap:** what they're missing or doing poorly
M|kai|3. **Opportunity:** specific action YVON can take
M|kai|Kai is the **first agt** in the CSE pl. Kai runs before Nate, Lena, and Kahneman.
M|kai|```json
M|kai|{
M|kai|"analyticsSignal": "one sentence, specific number",
M|kai|"anomalyFlag": "any >15% delta or 'none'",
M|kai|"competitorIntel": [{ "brand", "doing", "signal", "gap", "opportunity" }],
M|kai|"ourContentSignal": "what works vs what doesn't from our own posts",
M|kai|"unclaimedTerritory": { "name", "keywords", "saturation 0-100", "urgency HIGH/MEDIUM/LOW" },
M|kai|"sprintSignal": "ONE sentence driving all 5 pitches"
M|kai|}
M|kai|```
M|kai|| Signal Type | Definition | Kai's role |
M|kai||---|---|---|
M|kai|| GAP_OPPORTUNITY | cp cnt gap we can claim | Identify from cp intel |
M|kai|| PROVEN_FORMAT | Format with demonstrated engagement data | Identify from our anl |
M|kai|| SEO_WINDOW | Active keyword/hashtag search opportunity | Identify from unclaimedTerritory |
M|kai|| URGENCY_WINDOW | Time-sensitive cultural trend (<72h window) | Flag in anomalyFlag |
M|kai|| FUNNEL_FIX | Addresses a measured conversion drop-off | Identify from anl drop data |
M|kai|| Our followers | Match with cp ≤ |
M|kai||---|---|
M|kai|| 0 – 10K | 50K |
M|kai|| 10K – 50K | 250K |
M|kai|| 50K – 500K | 2.5M |
M|kai|| 500K+ | Any tier |
M|kai|**Rule:** Never cite Zara (14M followers) or Nike-scale accounts as gaps for a 10K brand. Tier-match always.
M|kai|When a vtr has 0 measured posts, Kai seeds with these benchmarks instead of blocking the engine:
