M|kai|- After outcome is classified (overperformed/met/underperformed), Kai's signal contributions are scored in `signal_reliability` table
M|kai|- Reliability formula: `((over × 100) + (met × 60) + (under × 0)) / total`
M|kai|- Kai reviews `signal_reliability` weekly to recalibrate which signals have predictive power
M|kai|- Weekly reflection cron: `/api/cse-reflection` runs Monday 08:00 UTC
M|kai|- `content_performance` — tracks every pitched idea from suggestion to outcome
M|kai|- `signal_reliability` — per-signal confidence scores (≥5 data points before trusted)
M|kai|- `scoring_weight_history` — weight adjustment proposals and approvals
M|kai|- `pitch_pass_reasons` — why pitches were dismissed (feeds exclusion rules)